interpretation: The "alarm clock" emoji signifies the need for urgency and time management. It reminds us that time is a precious commodity and we must make the most of it. This card may indicate that you have been procrastinating or have lost track of time and need to refocus your priorities. It may also suggest that you need to set clear boundaries and deadlines in order to achieve your goals. Pay attention to the details and stay organized in order to make the most of your time. This card can also symbolize the need for change or a wake-up call in your life. Trust your instincts and take action when necessary. Associated keywords include urgency, time management, deadlines, priorities, change, and wake-up call.
